<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="abc.css"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=utf-8" /><h1>Meet the Guys Who Want to Fund Your Franchise</h1>
				
					<img itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" alt="Meet the Guys Who Want to Fund Your Franchise" src="https://assets.entrepreneur.com/content/16x9/822/20160205225141-dan-murphy.png" rel="share" />

